DMAXUK.uk.description: Miami. The buyers are at Miami International Airport, home to 10,000 lost bags every year. Mark bids on bags of jewellery hoping to strike gold and Billy eyes up a heavy bag. S1, Ep1

DMAXUK.uk.title: Baggage Battles
DMAXUK.uk.description: London. Auction specialists fly across the Atlantic to bid on lost bags in London. Sally convinces Laurence to bid big and Mark and Billy compete to win interesting luggage. S1, Ep2

DMAXUK.uk.title: Baggage Battles
DMAXUK.uk.description: Cash Is King. The Baggage Battlers head to London, home to six airports, where Billy, Mark and the Martins compete for the lost and unclaimed bags of the rich passengers. S2, Ep3

DMAXUK.uk.title: Baggage Battles
DMAXUK.uk.description: California Scheming. The Baggage Battlers wage war at the crazy, eclectic Santa Cruz Lost Property Auction, where Mark brings in reinforcements to battle Billy over antique toys. S2, Ep9

DMAXUK.uk.title: Baggage Battles
DMAXUK.uk.description: Grand Theft Auto. The Baggage Battlers head to the Tampa Machinery Auction to bid on 1000's of lost or seized vehicles. But will they unearth any gems amongst the lot? S2, Ep10

DMAXUK.uk.title: Baggage Battles
DMAXUK.uk.description: Eye for an Eye. The Baggage Battlers are in Toronto for one of Canada's largest freight and baggage auctions. Billy makes one of his most shocking discoveries inside his winnings. S2, Ep11

DMAXUK.uk.title: Baggage Battles
DMAXUK.uk.description: Daredevils. The Baggage Battlers travel to Toronto to bid on international freight and baggage. One of the experts finds an item manufactured by legendary daredevil, Evel Knievel. S2, Ep12

DMAXUK.uk.title: Baggage Battles
DMAXUK.uk.description: Liar Liar. The Baggage Battlers attend a well-kept secret sheriff's auction in Shreveport, LA. Billy scores a touchdown with his winnings, while a local sheriff interrogates Mark. S2, Ep13

DMAXUK.uk.title: Baggage Battles
DMAXUK.uk.description: Shock & Awe. The Baggage Battlers heads to the Louisiana Farm auction to bid on Americana collected for over 50 years. Mark misfires when he bids on the wrong item. S2, Ep14

DMAXUK.uk.title: Baggage Battles
DMAXUK.uk.description: Bad Blood. The Baggage Battlers are back. Today they visit an auction in Red Hook, N.Y., to try to take home a piece of history. Will they succeed? S3, Ep1

DMAXUK.uk.title: Junkyard Empire
DMAXUK.uk.description: Up In Smoke. Andy and Tim take on a professional drifting course, while Blair tackles a luxurious, yet smoking, 2013 Audi A8L. Dave installs a new rear end on Andy's '66 Nova. S5, Ep7

DMAXUK.uk.title: Junkyard Empire
DMAXUK.uk.description: Money's On The Finish Line. Andy buys a stolen and stripped Porsche C4S at an auction, but Bobby has his doubts. Dave works overtime to beef up a '57 Belair for a drag race. S5, Ep8

DMAXUK.uk.title: Junkyard Empire
DMAXUK.uk.description: Cashin' In. Between tracking down body parts for the stripped Porsche and helping a client modernize a vintage hot rod, Andy has fallen behind - and Bob's not happy! S5, Ep9

DMAXUK.uk.title: Junkyard Empire
DMAXUK.uk.description: Toys For Big Boys. A '68 RS SS Camaro hasn't run in more than 20 years, but now it's time to turn the former cover car into a 1,200 horsepower street car. S5, Ep10

DMAXUK.uk.title: Kindig Customs
DMAXUK.uk.description: Meet Judge Kevdogg. Normally when Kindig-It Design attends a car show, their cars are the ones being judged. This time, Dave and Kev select the top 10 builders at a show. S8, Ep3

DMAXUK.uk.title: Kindig Customs
DMAXUK.uk.description: Restorations? We're Talking 'Bout Restorations? Dave takes on a restoration for clients celebrating their 25th anniversary. They've owned the car since they got married. S8, Ep4

DMAXUK.uk.title: Kindig Customs
DMAXUK.uk.description: It's A Barn Door Deluxe, Of Course. Dave has done double-cab VWs, Bugs, and Karmann Ghias, but now he is taking on something completely different - and even more rare. S8, Ep5

DMAXUK.uk.title: Texas Metal
DMAXUK.uk.description: Denali Drop. Bill customises a brand new 2018 Yukon Denali by dropping it to the floor on 28x15 wheels, all while keeping the third-row seats for the client's family. S2, Ep1

DMAXUK.uk.title: Texas Metal
DMAXUK.uk.description: Buckin' Bronco. Bill and the team transform a rusted '68 Bronco roadster into a high-powered off-roading truck with a supercharged engine, roll cage and waterproof interior. S2, Ep2

DMAXUK.uk.title: Expedition Bigfoot
DMAXUK.uk.description: Low Tide, High Danger. After being stalked and hearing strange whistles, Ronny and Mireya launch a sound trap. Bryce learns a witness was withholding terrifying information. S4, Ep5

DMAXUK.uk.title: Expedition Bigfoot
DMAXUK.uk.description: Tracking Terror. Strange sounds lead to a disturbing discovery for Ronny and Mireya. Russell tracks a mysterious creature. Bryce hears screams near the target zone. S4, Ep6

DMAXUK.uk.title: Alaska Monsters
DMAXUK.uk.description: Bigfoot of Cache Creek: Woodsman. The AMS team trespass on gold claims to investigate a Bigfoot reported to be responsible for the notorious unsolved murders in the Cache Creek. S2, Ep5

DMAXUK.uk.title: Alaska Monsters
DMAXUK.uk.description: Bigfoot of Copper Valley: Red Devil. After discovering a dangerous alpha Bigfoot leading a tree clan, the team designs a Bed of Nails Trap to capture the aggressive leader. S2, Ep6

DMAXUK.uk.title: Expedition X
DMAXUK.uk.description: Avalanche Ghost Train. At the site of America's deadliest avalanche, witnesses report bizarre apparitions and feelings of dread. Phil and Jess test a mind-bending scientific theory. S3, Ep8

DMAXUK.uk.title: Expedition X
DMAXUK.uk.description: Mexico's Haunted Cenotes. Phil and Jess investigate caverns believed to be portals to the Maya underworld. The sacred cenotes supposedly hide secrets far darker than any legend. S3, Ep9

DMAXUK.uk.title: Expedition X
DMAXUK.uk.description: Ring Of Fire UFOs. Phil and Jess probe the science behind geology's strangest phenomena while investigating mysterious objects flying around Mexico's tallest active volcano. S3, Ep10

DMAXUK.uk.title: Baggage Battles
DMAXUK.uk.description: Atlanta. The buyers are in Atlanta to bid on items at an unclaimed freight auction. Billy and Mark are interested in military items and the Martins discover an unusual find! S1, Ep4

DMAXUK.uk.title: Gold Divers
DMAXUK.uk.description: Naked And Unafraid Part 1. The revamped Myrtle Irene is back in action and on the hunt for gold. Vernon gives Steve another opportunity, and Kris finally finds some gold. S10, Ep11

DMAXUK.uk.title: Gold Divers
DMAXUK.uk.description: Naked And Unafraid Part 2. Shawn weighs gold from the Myrtle Irene's first run of the season - will it live up to his expectations? Meanwhile, Zeke's brother returns to diving. S10, Ep12

DMAXUK.uk.title: Aussie Gold Hunters
DMAXUK.uk.description: The Dust Devils' operation halts and the hold-up could cost them thousands of dollars. A cyclone causes damage to Shane and Russell's wash plant. S5, Ep16

DMAXUK.uk.title: Outback Crystal Hunters
DMAXUK.uk.description: From The Pinnacle To The Pit. Jarrin and Hugh hunt for anything and everything in the walls of their mine. The Neils risk life and limb against deadly boulders at 'Topaz Mountain'. S2, Ep8

DMAXUK.uk.title: Deadliest Catch
DMAXUK.uk.description: Captain Conflict. Sig races to offload his tanks before losing half a million dollars in crab. Plus, tension between co-captains reaches breaking point in the Wizard's wheelhouse. S14, Ep13

DMAXUK.uk.title: Deadliest Catch
DMAXUK.uk.description: Baptism By Fire. It's baptism by fire aboard the Northwestern as Mandy takes her first shift in heavy seas. Plus, the Wizard crew battles over one man who isn't pulling his weight. S14, Ep14

DMAXUK.uk.title: Blowing Up History
DMAXUK.uk.description: Tower Of Babel: The New Evidence. The Tower of Babel is one of the most famous stories of the Bible. Archaeologists use new technology to uncover how engineers could have built it. S4, Ep16

DMAXUK.uk.title: Expedition Unknown
DMAXUK.uk.description: City Of Gold. Josh treks the Inca Trail through the Andes and into the Peruvian Amazon in search of a mythical city of gold. His journey takes a detour to the ruins of Machu Picchu. S1, Ep5

DMAXUK.uk.title: Expedition Unknown
DMAXUK.uk.description: Captain Morgan's Lost Gold. Josh dives into the Lajas Reef in search of the treasure of legendary pirate Henry Morgan. His journey takes him to a modern marvel, the Panama Canal. S1, Ep6

DMAXUK.uk.title: Homestead Rescue: Raney Ranch
DMAXUK.uk.description: Fire On The Forty. An inferno engulfs Marty and Mollee's cabin at the onset of winter, and the Raneys rush to complete the unfinished clifftop cabin with heat, water and power. S1, Ep9

DMAXUK.uk.title: Homestead Rescue: Raney Ranch
DMAXUK.uk.description: On Thin Ice. Marty attempts a treacherous trip across a frozen river. And, Misty and Maciah build a pump house to secure the family's new water source on the Upper 20. S1, Ep10

DMAXUK.uk.title: Outback Opal Hunters
DMAXUK.uk.description: The Bishop hires a bomb expert to blast the impenetrable rock that's blocking access to a rich opal seam. Meanwhile, the Misfits face avalanches and dust storms. S5, Ep10

DMAXUK.uk.title: Outback Opal Hunters
DMAXUK.uk.description: The Mooka Boys risk being buried alive as they hunt for a legendary mine shaft. The Blacklighters are overwhelmed by choking dust on their bone-dry claim. S5, Ep11

DMAXUK.uk.title: Deadliest Catch
DMAXUK.uk.description: The Better Captain. With $1 million in crab at stake, the Wizard battles unrelenting waves. Jake strikes bargain to aid another captain, but it may come at a cost. S19, Ep14

DMAXUK.uk.title: Deadliest Catch
DMAXUK.uk.description: Uncharted Grounds. Winter unleashes its fury on the fleet. When Keith's winch seizes, the Wizard crew work a double shift to retrieve their pots. Plus, the Summer Bay runs aground. S19, Ep15

DMAXUK.uk.title: Body Bizarre
DMAXUK.uk.description: Born As One Sister. Conjoined twins Erika and Eva Sandoval undergo a 17-hour surgery. Wells Middleton battles through his new future after losing both his hands. S8, Ep1

DMAXUK.uk.title: Body Bizarre
DMAXUK.uk.description: The Worst Disease You've Never Heard Of. 15-year-old John suffers from epidermolysis bullosa and has no indication of how long he might live. Justice suffers from a rare sleep condition. S8, Ep2

DMAXUK.uk.title: Aussie Gold Hunters
DMAXUK.uk.description: The Gold Devils set their sights on a record-breaking total. Plus, a gold drought causes one member of the Poseidon Crew to question his future. S8, Ep1

DMAXUKPlus1.uk.title: Richard Hammond's Workshop
DMAXUKPlus1.uk.description: Crunch Time. After a disastrous test with the MGB, Richard warns the Cogs if they can't turn things around in time for the next race, he'll ditch the whole project. S3, Ep5

DMAXUKPlus1.uk.title: Richard Hammond's Workshop
DMAXUKPlus1.uk.description: Wheels And Waves. The Cogs go international restoring an iconic 1970s Royal Enfield Interceptor motorbike. An epic road trip ensues when they take the bike to Biarritz. S3, Ep6

DMAXUKPlus1.uk.title: Aussie Gold Hunters
DMAXUKPlus1.uk.description: The Poseidon Crew's mine site is swamped after a brutal storm. Ryan collapses in a deadly heatwave, while Russell and Shane uncover a big nugget. S7, Ep20

DMAXUKPlus1.uk.title: Naked And Afraid
DMAXUKPlus1.uk.description: Worlds Collide. Former military man, Chance, is paired with naturalist, Melissa, in the Amazon jungle. Humidity, violent storms, caiman, and red-bellied piranha hit them hard. S3, Ep7

DMAXUKPlus1.uk.title: Naked And Afraid
DMAXUKPlus1.uk.description: The Hunted. A country boy teams up with a mother of four and they are dropped into the jaguar-filled jungle of Belize. But, while they hunt for food, something is hunting them. S3, Ep8

DMAXUKPlus1.uk.title: Salvage Dawgs
DMAXUKPlus1.uk.description: Trenton Central High School. The team take on a huge high school in Trenton, New Jersey. Key items include fireclay sinks and oak cabinets. Plus, Mike and Tay build an N-shaped desk. S5, Ep5

DMAXUKPlus1.uk.title: Salvage Dawgs
DMAXUKPlus1.uk.description: Portside Marina. The guys save the bow and stern of a boat on Smith Mountain Lake in Moneta, Virginia. And, new team members Molly May and Stella make their debut. S5, Ep6

DMAXUKPlus1.uk.title: Deadliest Catch
DMAXUKPlus1.uk.description: Fire At Sea: Part 2. Alone on the water, days from land, the Northwestern catches fire. On the Time Bandit, a family emergency forces Johnathan to make a desperate move. S12, Ep14

DMAXUKPlus1.uk.title: Deadliest Catch
DMAXUKPlus1.uk.description: Blood & Guts. Winter rages on. There's bloodshed on the Time Bandit, a fight breaks out on the Wizard and a lost bet leads to cod guts on the Brenna A. S12, Ep15

DMAXUKPlus1.uk.title: Deadliest Catch
DMAXUKPlus1.uk.description: Life Or Death Decision. A rogue wave forces Zack to make a life-or-death decision. Meanwhile, Josh bets on a Bering Sea myth, and Sig turns to daughter Mandy for help. S12, Ep16

DMAXUKPlus1.uk.title: Deadliest Catch: Inside the Catch: Best Brawls
DMAXUKPlus1.uk.description: Takes a closer look at the feuds and short fuses that make up the best Deadliest Catch conflicts. On a crab boat, sometimes the only way to earn respect is to fight for it.

DMAXUKPlus1.uk.title: Outback Opal Hunters
DMAXUKPlus1.uk.description: Risky Business. Justin gambles thousands of dollars as he is struggling this season. Kelly is in desperate need for a big find underground and Aaron and Greg's claim might pay off. S2, Ep4

DMAXUKPlus1.uk.title: Outback Opal Hunters
DMAXUKPlus1.uk.description: Hot Hot Heat. The Rookies' relationship is on the rocks as they battle their biggest claim yet. With two partners working at different speeds, there's a fight brewing. S2, Ep5

DMAXUKPlus1.uk.title: Outback Opal Hunters
DMAXUKPlus1.uk.description: Machine Mayhem. It's the last chance for the Rookies' partnership. Meanwhile, the Cooke brothers fight busted hoses and breakdowns in their quest to strike it rich. S2, Ep6

DMAXUKPlus1.uk.title: Outback Crystal Hunters
DMAXUKPlus1.uk.description: Crystal Climax. In the final week of the season, Patrick gets an offer for their million-dollar Amethyst cluster while his team race to unearth $200,000 of crystals. S1, Ep8

DMAXUKPlus1.uk.title: Outback Crystal Hunters
DMAXUKPlus1.uk.description: Aqua Hues And Sapphire Blues. Patrick Gundersen's team tackles harsh terrain in the hunt for aquamarine. Plus, the Rubyvale Boys battle against mechanical malfunctions. S2, Ep1

DMAXUKPlus1.uk.title: Outback Crystal Hunters
DMAXUKPlus1.uk.description: Safety Thongs. Newcomer, Neil Wilkinson Jr., abseils down a deadly mineshaft in search of cubic fluorite, while Jarrin and Hugh take the plunge into frigid waters. S2, Ep2

DMAXUKPlus1.uk.title: Aussie Gold Hunters
DMAXUKPlus1.uk.description: The Gold Devils return to their Fair lady lease hoping to reach their target before the season ends. Meanwhile, the Ferals suffer a major setback. S8, Ep17

DMAXUKPlus1.uk.title: Aussie Gold Hunters
DMAXUKPlus1.uk.description: The Poseidon Crew face intense pressure when a police incident pulls Ethan away. Plus, Alan and Salty brave uncharted waters in search of sunken treasure. S8, Ep18

DMAXUKPlus1.uk.title: Aussie Gold Hunters
DMAXUKPlus1.uk.description: Jacqui and Andrew face a major setback and enlist the help of a rookie miner to reach their season target. Alan and Salty gamble on a front-end loader. S8, Ep19

DMAXUKPlus1.uk.title: Hoarding: Buried Alive
DMAXUKPlus1.uk.description: My House Can Kill Me. Miranda's obsession has left her children with no room to play whilst Hsi-Ming's daughter worries over her mother's health. S3, Ep11

DMAXUKPlus1.uk.title: Hoarding: Buried Alive
DMAXUKPlus1.uk.description: Owned by the Roaches. Celia is a psychologist who can't solve her own hoarding problem. Now she's losing the battle against her stuff and the roaches infesting her home. S3, Ep12

DMAXUKPlus1.uk.title: I Was Bitten
DMAXUKPlus1.uk.description: Alligator And Rattlesnake. Botfly maggots live under Evan's skin and eat his flesh. When Kasey swims across a canal for a dare, he is dragged into a death roll by an alligator. S1, Ep4

DMAXUKPlus1.uk.title: I Was Bitten
DMAXUKPlus1.uk.description: Tiger, Elephant And Snake. State-of-the-art science goes behind near-fatal bites to reveal how the individuals who faced deadly snakes and a 9000-pound elephant managed to survive. S1, Ep5

DMAXUKPlus1.uk.title: My New Face: Body Bizarre
DMAXUKPlus1.uk.description: My New Face. In Mexico, Adrian, 22, has a basketball-sized tumour on the side of his face. In the US Janice has a giant leg that has grown out of proportion to the rest of her body. S6, Ep12

DMAXUKPlus1.uk.title: Body Bizarre
DMAXUKPlus1.uk.description: Little Dany's First Smile. In Mexico Dany, 8, was born with Moebius Syndrome which paralysed her face. She's set to undergo delicate microsurgery. Will she smile for the first time? S6, Ep13

DMAXUKPlus1.uk.title: Body Bizarre
DMAXUKPlus1.uk.description: My Body Is Eating Itself. Lee, 42, from England, has a rare stomach disorder that means his body is eating itself. In Columbia, Edward is just 70cm tall. Can a specialist explain it? S6, Ep14

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Planet Earth
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Seasonal Forests: David Attenborough narrates this series about the world's ecosystems. Enjoy a look at some amazing woodlands, such as the strange baobab forests of Madagascar. S1 Ep8

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Planet Earth
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Jungles: David Attenborough's acclaimed natural history series. Learn about tropical rainforests, which cover just three per cent of the world yet are home to half of its species. S1 Ep9

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Planet Earth
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Shallow Seas: David Attenborough celebrates our amazing planet. Here we follow a humpback whale and its calf on a journey from a tropical paradise to storm-ravaged icy polar seas. S1 Ep10

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Simon Reeve's South America
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: In the third part of his journey, Simon Reeve travels through the Andes mountains from Peru to Bolivia, beginning at the world-famous ruins of Machu Pichu. S1 Ep3

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Robson Green: World's Most Amazing Walks
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Normandy Beaches, France: An emotional Robson walks along the north coast of Normandy in France to trace the footsteps of brave soldiers of the D-Day landings. S1 Ep3

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Flipping Bangers
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: MGB: Gus and Will want to buy an MGB roadster but the cheaper GT version is the one they find. It's got a few rust patches, and back in the workshop they realise beauty is skin deep. S2 Ep1

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash: Restoring Classics
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Land Rover 90 / Caravan: The team, including Andy Joynson, buy the right kind of Land Rover, but it's got the wrong engine. Can they clean up its emissions with a modern motor? S7 Ep6

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Rover SD1/Jag 240: Derek collects a Mark 2 Jag and explains why they made such poor getaway cars for bank robbers. A customer considers a Morris Marina as a present for his wife. S1 Ep7

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: AC Cobra/Volvo F8T8: The team have a record number of cars to auction, but Derek finds room for one more - a replica AC Cobra. A couple are reunited with their Volvo breakdown truck. S1 Ep8

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: E Type S2/Escort RS Turbo: A classic car fan with a love of the Jaguar E-Type reluctantly sends his dream car to auction, hoping to buy a motorhome. Two Ford Escorts get Dave's pulse racing. S1 Ep9

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Rolls Silver Shadow/Austin 7: A widow reluctantly parts with her husband's treasured collection of Rolls Royces and Bentleys, and an impulse buyer finds one of the cars a new home. S1 Ep10

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Teleshopping
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Shopping from Home.

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Great British Railway Journeys
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Elgin to Loch Ness: Michael Portillo visits Lossiemouth and Inverness. His journey ends at Loch Ness, where he joins a Deep Scan research team searching for the elusive monster. S11 Ep5

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Great British Railway Journeys
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: St Ives to St Day: Michael Portillo explores the West Country between the wars, setting off from the Cornish seaside resort of St Ives and ending in the former mining village of St Day. S11 Ep6

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Great British Railway Journeys
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Truro to St Mawgan: Michael Portillo visits Cornwall's county town, Truro, heading to the historic estate of Trewithen, whose gardens were stocked from China by plant hunters. S11 Ep7

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Great British Railway Journeys
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Bodmin to Totnes: Michael Portillo reaches Bodmin en route to Totnes, as he explores the West Country from St Ives to Salisbury Plain, learning more about Daphne du Maurier on the way. S11 Ep8

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Austin Gipsy / Toyota MR2 Ferrari: Derek heads to Scotland in a rainstorm to pick up a Jaguar E-type and a rare MGC convertible, and Dave extracts a rare Austin Gipsey from a lock-up. S5 Ep3

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Ford Thames 400E/Vauxhall Astra: Derek collects a Ford Thames 400E that once belonged to the pop band Edison Lighthouse. Plus, Dave heads to York to collect an Astra GTE convertible. S5 Ep4

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: War Factories
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: General Motors: How the Americans, once they were provoked into war, out-produced the rest of the world so quickly and by such a huge margin, including the likes of General Motors. S1 Ep4

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: The World at War
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Red Star: Following Operation Barbarossa in 1941, the Soviet Army battled the Germans almost alone for two years. Laurence Olivier recounts their efforts as the epic series continues. S1 Ep11

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Antiques Roadshow
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Compilation - Abbotsford and Burghley: Fiona Bruce presents assessments of items not initially shown in programmes from Abbotsford and Burghley. S32 Ep26

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Antiques Roadshow
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Chester: The team returns to Chester Cathedral, where objects include a sheriff's ring of office, hand-carved wooden shoes and a painting that has been left lying under a bed. S32 Ep27

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Jaguar 2+2 E Type: Paul's on a big day out collecting a 1971 Jaguar E-Type and a 1933 Morgan 3-wheeler Supersport but first there's a flock of 300 chickens to negotiate before he can load up. S7 Ep11

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Subaru Impreza: Dave's in fast car heaven as he picks up a rare Subaru Impreza and an equally powerful Ford Escort RS Cosworth from North Wales. S7 Ep12

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: War Factories
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: General Motors: How the Americans, once they were provoked into war, out-produced the rest of the world so quickly and by such a huge margin, including the likes of General Motors. S1 Ep4

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: The World at War
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Red Star: Following Operation Barbarossa in 1941, the Soviet Army battled the Germans almost alone for two years. Laurence Olivier recounts their efforts as the epic series continues. S1 Ep11

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Antiques Roadshow
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: British Museum 2: The experts return to the British Museum, where items brought in by members of the public include photos of a young Elvis Presley. S33 Ep21

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Canal Boat Diaries
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Loughborough to Braunston: Robbie Cumming has problems with ice on the Grand Union Canal, and ends his journey in Braunston, Northamptonshire. S4 Ep4

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Canal Boat Diaries
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Shardlow to Stoke-on-Trent: Robbie Cumming journeys from Shardlow to Etruria Junction, Stoke on Trent, exploring the Trent and Mersey Canal. S1 Ep1

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: New: Robson Green: World's Most Amazing Walks
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Great Glen Way, Scotland: Robson hikes the Great Glen Way in Scotland, a staggering rift valley that cuts through the Highlands from the foot of Ben Nevis to Loch Ness. S1 Ep4

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Ireland with Simon Reeve
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Starting at the Giant's Causeway, Simon travels down the east coast to the rapidly changing cities of Belfast and Dublin before ending his tour in the Wicklow Mountains. S1 Ep2

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Jaguar 2+2 E Type: Paul's on a big day out collecting a 1971 Jaguar E-Type and a 1933 Morgan 3-wheeler Supersport but first there's a flock of 300 chickens to negotiate before he can load up. S7 Ep11
